name: ext_R4B_ObservationDefinition_qualifiedInterval

description: This cross-version extension represents ObservationDefinition.qualifiedInterval from http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/ObservationDefinition|4.3.0 for use in FHIR R5.

element.short: Qualified range for continuous and ordinal observation results
